- You look
just like your father.

00:16:26.004 --> 00:16:27.540
Same eyes.

00:16:27.640 --> 00:16:29.742
You've got Harry's eyes.

00:16:30.510 --> 00:16:32.010
- Have I?

00:16:32.712 --> 00:16:34.547
- Where is Harry?

