I told him,
I said, "That's rude."

00:27:13.452 --> 00:27:15.221
- That's very rude.

00:27:15.254 --> 00:27:16.789
- Morning, Nan.

00:27:18.791 --> 00:27:21.360
- I didn't know.
I would've stopped it.

00:27:22.695 --> 00:27:24.730
Always at night,

00:27:24.997 --> 00:27:27.366
creeping around,
hidden in the shadows.

00:27:27.399 --> 00:27:28.801
- Oh yeah.

