Your gran's symptoms
can really mess with your head.

00:34:17.276 --> 00:34:19.077
Yeah.

00:34:19.879 --> 00:34:21.748
Look at you you're freezing.
- Yeah.

00:34:21.781 --> 00:34:23.816
- Go and get warm
and dry, darling.

